Package: descriptio
Type: Package
Title: A Toolbox for Descriptive Statistical Analysis
Version: 1.0
Author: Nicolas Robette
Maintainer: Nicolas Robette <nicolas.robette@uvsq.fr>
Imports: MASS, ggplot2, rlang, ggpattern 
Suggests: rmarkdown, knitr, rmdformats, paletteer, GGally, vcd
Description: Provides functions for the description of statistical associations between two variables : measures of local and global association between variables (phi, Cramer's V, point-biserial correlation, eta-squared, Goodman & Kruskal tau, PEM, etc.), multiple graphical representations of the associations between two variables (using ggplot2), weighted statistics and permutation tests.
VignetteBuilder: knitr, rmarkdown
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
URL: https://github.com/nicolas-robette/descriptio, https://nicolas-robette.github.io/descriptio/
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.1
